<table cellspacing="0" class="contact">

<tr>
<th>Editorial&nbsp;Feedback</th>
<td>
We want to  <a href="/news/feedback/mail">hear your thoughts</a> on our news coverage.<br />
<em><strong>Note:</strong> We may publish your e-mail in our <a href="/news/rants/">Rants &amp; Raves</a> letters-to-the-editor section. If you do <em>not</em> wish to see your message published, please let us know in your letter.</em>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<th>Site Fix</th>
<td>
If you want to report a broken link or technical problems with our site, send a message to our <a href="/news/feedback/mail/1,2330,2,00.html">production team</a>.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<th>Tips &amp; Pitches</th>
<td>
Have a scoop or tip? We'd like to <a href="/news/feedback/mail/1,2330,3,00.html">hear about it</a>. To pitch an idea, use our <a href="/news/feedback/mail/1,2330,5,00.html">story pitch form</a>. Please read our <a href="/news/pitching/">pitching guidelines</a> first.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<th><cite>Wired</cite>&nbsp;magazine</th>
<td>
<p>For queries about an existing subscription visit the magazine's <a href="/wired/subscribe/service.html">customer service page</a>.</p>
<p>For new <cite>Wired</cite> magazine subscriptions e-mail <a href="mailto:subscriptions@wiredmag.com">subscriptions@wiredmag.com</a> or call 800-SOWIRED (800-769-4733) inside the U.S. and Canada or 303-678-0354 from all other countries.</p>
</td>
</tr>


