<h2>Get Wired News Your Way</h2>
<p>
Typing www.wired.com into your browser is not the only way to get Wired News. And it's not the only easy way, either. Whether you want to download our latest news to your handheld, subscribe to e-mail alerts, or add a Wired News toolbar to your browser, we've got a <a href="/news/members">bucketful of options</a> for you.
</p>
